{"tid":470604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【契弟李華明】永遠擺食喜得佳","createTime":"2017-11-16T12:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T05:29:53.000Z","uid":37528,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9f6cae3e6a84f152dcec1a849dfe198fb7ec8595","tid":470604,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T12:33:15.000Z","msg":"李華明轟「台港連線」觸動中央　避用「回歸」字眼<br />\n<br />\n李華明：相當離奇的案件　稱一直半信半疑　憂民主黨公信力再「插水」<br />\n<br />\n李華明批青年反叛幼稚「令我們蒙羞」　指從無「港人民族」<br />\n<br />\n李華明批朱凱廸動議不負責任　指政治原則是妥協、談判<br />\n<br />\n前立法會議員李華明(肥仔明)今天(14日)與太太現身ICC，原來他們趁將軍澳有新樓盤推出，特意去買樓，太太更抽中1個3房望海單位，售價約1000萬港元。肥仔明女兒3年前才入手同屬將軍澳的單位，似乎他們一家無懼辣招，用盡名額入市。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/203240_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F203240_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e0d37319&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食屎啦，賤種走狗契弟明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13109c7a0c7cdc1e88419d4ceb5317a0032a8d26","tid":470604,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T12:34:37.000Z","msg":"乜撚野on9公司，搵條契弟賣廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738ad4c4977f7adc745f2eeb8ca59db8047a168b","tid":470604,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T12:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59aa56a43be7486ac779cfe332197c39fc000356","tid":470604,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T13:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbbc4ede2cf279315c57ebfe24a8a28aac7c935a","tid":470604,"uid":22858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T13:47:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>賣港匯點冚家多重癌症<br />\n<br />\n五毛係咪好驚下個到你就無糧出</strong></s